&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI Azumano &lt;/strong&gt;is seeking an Accounting Clerk&amp;nbsp;to support our growing team. This position is remote.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Accounting Clerk performs accounting and clerical functions to support accounting operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Responsibilities include, but are not limited to&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Processing and reconciling ARC data, which acts as the central system for airline ticket reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide accounting and clerical functions to support the finance department&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform all necessary account, bank and other reconciliations&lt;/li&gt;
