&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great Hill&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Azure Cloud&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;in Orlando, FL. The Azure Cloud Engineer will support cloud modernization and Test &amp;amp; Evaluation (T&amp;amp;E) initiatives through the implementation, sustainment, and security management of Azure Government cloud environments supporting mission-critical Department of Defense training, experimentation, and distributed test operations.&lt;/p&gt;
