&lt;p&gt;The position requires a highly technical engineer capable of operating in both unclassified and classified environments while maintaining compliance with Risk Management Framework (RMF), Authority to Operate (ATO), cybersecurity, and configuration management requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
