&lt;li&gt;Minimum of two years of program management experience for a University, Major Corporate Division, or Small Business. Demonstrated recent experience working in program operational and logistical functions such as event planning and coordination, administrative and clerical support functions. Recent experience is defined as within the last two years.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Secret Level Clearance required to start.&lt;/li&gt;
